author: Taegan Goddard
title: Most Democrats Say Clinton Won Debate
text:
Most Democrats Say Clinton Won Debate October 15, 2015 By Taegan Goddard 0 Comments 
A HuffPost/YouGov poll finds 55% of registered Democratic voters who watched the first Democratic debate said Hillary Clinton won. 
Sen. Bernie Sanders, who saw a surge in online interest and fundraising after the debate, was a distant second, with only 22% saying he was the best of the night.
